EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 1800Z DAILY
   30 NOV THRU 03 DEC WITHIN 25 MILES OF:
   A. 57-45N 009-16W.
   B. 57-11N 008-53W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 031900Z DEC.
